Booking the certification
(4/9)
Block the calendar. Although it is very subjective, this has been found to be very effective among those preparing for the exam. Booking the certification helps a lot of people get serious about preparation. What if you were busy with other commitments and could not prepare? As long as you are 48 hours before the certification, you can reschedule it to a comfortable date. You can use the following link to book the certification . This will take you to to register for the certification.